1.0.name: wordpress/persian-world
1.0.description:
It will turn WordPress [en_US] into Persian [fa_IR] and also have most awesome features you should have on Persian WordPress !

Features

  • "Fully compatible with latest WordPress version
  • "Fully UTF-8 conversion.
  • "Adds two buttons to the TinyMCE editor [LTR and RTL directions.]
  • "Enables Usernames containing Persian characters [Default Wordpress does not allow to use persian characters in usernames]
  • "Changes the Font-Family of TinyMCE editor in admin panel to Tahoma 15px. [It's not effects your website design.]

Includes

  • Default MO file [fa_IR]
  • Admin MO file [admin-fa_IR]
  • Admin-network MO file [admin-network-fa_IR]
  • MCE [css]

What's Next?

This plugin is Under Development. Please try it and contact me (
